channel.title: Making a runescape private server?! [317] the whole package [317]
channel.description:
:) hey guys, i typed all of this out on notepad to show you how to make your own runescape private server, this is only for 317 servers though! i will be coming up with another on how to make 508's
INCLUDES:
~ Getting a good source ~ Changing player rights ~ Coding your server ~ Creating Compiler.bat (optional) ~ Setting up No-ip ~ portForwarding ~ putting server online
DOWNLOAD LINK:: http://www.megaupload.com/?d=Z2O31ECF
thanks, leave a comment! (note): this was all typed out and written by 100% me!! ;D
